Package: tslibR
Title: R Client for the tslib Time-Series REST API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Navdeep", "Gill",
    email = "navdeep.gill@servicenow.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A thin httr2-based wrapper around the tslib REST API, providing
    access to time-series forecasting (ARIMA, SARIMA, ARIMAX, VAR, ETS,
    state-space), decomposition (STL), evaluation, transforms, stationarity
    tests, and data-quality endpoints from R. Matches the Python tslib client
    surface and is installable via devtools::install_github().
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports:
    httr2 (>= 1.0.0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    webmockr (>= 0.9.0),
    jsonlite (>= 1.8.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/navdeep-G/tslib
